Вакансія від 16 березня 2020
Sales Manager in Logistics
Hegelmann Transporte
Транспорт, логістика;
більше 1000 співробітників
Київ, проспект Степана Бандери, 9.
5,5 км від центру ·
На мапі
Андрей Лановик ·
Показати телефон
Повна зайнятість.
Вища освіта.
Опис вакансії
YOUR MAIN TASKS:They optimize processes for the internal and external sales forceThey serve existing customers and expand customer relationshipsThey conduct price negotiations and check contract contentsThey independently and purposefully acquire new customersYou create offers with subsequent follow-upYOUR REQUIREMENT PROFILE:You have successfully completed a commercial education and work experience in salesYou speak German, English (at least B2 level) and another foreign language are an advantageYou work in a structured way and think in a process-oriented wayYou are confident and can convince by your particular natureThey are able to motivate themselves and to work independentlyYOUR ADVANTAGES:A full-time job and promotion opportunities in an international transport companyResponsible activities with short decision-making in a well-rehearsed teamThe development of your personal and professional skills
